# Accounting Copilot — Cursor rules

Read `/AGENTS.md` before coding.

## Must know

- Monorepo: UI in `app/src/`, Rust in `app/src-tauri/`.
- App data id: `com.moonmaxtea.accounting-copilot`.
- Vite `base` must stay `"./"` (Tauri production).
- Download progress: Tauri IPC `Channel`, not event-only listeners.
- Private GitHub updates: token → `api.github.com` in `update.rs`.
- If `pack.loaded == false`, user has no standards pack installed.
- UI copy is English; no third-party editor names in product UI.
- Continue (Follow-up): use `config::relative_project_path`; debug via `ai-debug.log` (`continue_requested` → `agent_continue`).

## Commands

```bash
pnpm test
cd app/src-tauri && cargo test
pnpm app:dev
pnpm app:build
```

## Branches

`cursor/<descriptive-name>-1b98` off `main`. Never commit secrets.
